disease treatment in Chitwan.\n\nCoronavirus patients from across the country are coming to the hospitals in the district for the treatment.","title":"Plasma bank set up for treatment of critical COVID-19 patients - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/11/126621/","video":[]}
